# Mum's Waffles


## Ingredients

    2 eggs (room temperature)
    1½ cups milk (room temperature)
    ¼ cup melted butter
    1½ cups flour
    2 tbsp sugar
    3 tsp baking powder
    ½ tsp salt
    
## Instructions

1. Mix the wet ingredients until well combined. 
2. Add the sugar and salt and mixed until dissolved.
3. Add the flour and baking powder and beat only until smooth. 
4. Heat waffle iron as directed and cook until golden brown.

### Notes

- Recipe Mum makes every other weekend.

